@NODE Y1 "SpellData"

TELEPORTATION OF TRAVELLING
---------------------------
	Teleports your caster to a place choosed by you. The place must be
a square which you have already seen, that is, visible on your map. Riders
cannot teleport their horses, neither can horses teleport with their riders.
(Like magic-user centaurs) You can not teleport inside solide substance,
neither can you teleport on top of somebody.

@ENDNODE

