BIG BLAST OF COLOSSAL CHARRING
------------------------------

	A tremendous explosion of a very wide area. The only drawback is the
quite small amount of damage, but it doesn't decrease very quickly - making it 
almost as effective through its whole area. 

@ENDNODE

