POSSESSION OF PATHETIC BASTARDS
-------------------------------
	With this spell you are able to convert enemy characters into friendly
ones! The ones you try to possess can try to resist this spell. The more 
intelligent they are, the more difficult they are to possess.

@ENDNODE

