@NODE FUTURE "Future"

	The next version, 1.3 or something, will have a better graphic interface.
That means, that the main-screen gfx have been redrawn. The game window will be
larger, and there is more space for the itemboxes and the text-box, too.

	The date of the 1.3 version is currently unknown.
	
	The next project after the 1.3 version is rumoured to be to start
developing the scenario-editor. It will be very simple at first, but might be
improved afterwards. 

	The map editor will propably be separate from the scenario-editor. That is
because the map editor is by now quite functional, and developing the scenario
editor on top of it does not seem to be a good idea. 

@ENDNODE

